ns of, like, =E2=80=9Cif we sell shares to the public at $10 and buy our sh=
ares at $2 then we=E2=80=99ll get=C2=A0rich=E2=80=9D:Since the SPAC Busines=
s Agreement gave Shevland the right to invest up to equal amounts as Orland=
o at the same price per share, Shevland repeatedly asked Orlando the share =
