 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Bloomberg=E2=80=99s tra=
nscript</a> of Saylor=E2=80=99s remarks:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">This is what differentiates a operating company from just a finan=
